  "text": "3 H]Methyllycaconitine (MLA) binding to ␣7 nAChRs was determined in hippocampal membranes as described previously [CITATION_1] . The IC 50 (concentration of the compound that produces 50% inhibition of binding) was determined by least-squares nonlinear regression using GraphPad Prism software (GraphPad Software Inc., San Diego, CA). K i was calculated using the Cheng-Prusoff equation [CITATION_2] .",
